com.esri.mo2.cs.geom
Interface Polygon

All Superinterfaces:
ClementiniGeometry, Cloneable, FeatureGeometry, Geometry, GeometryCollection, HitTest, PointApplicatorUser, SegmentHitTest, Shape
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasePolygon, Envelope
public interface Polygon
extends FeatureGeometry, HitTest, SegmentHitTest

Implements a collection of one or more Rings. Each Ring represents an "interior" or "exterior" boundary for the shape as a whole. A Polygon with a single Ring is a simple polygon. A Polygon can contain multiple interior and/or exterior rings.

See Also:
Ring
